reviews.review_text: Incredible recording! Best Dead show I ever attended! Maybe not a classic overall but the sound and the crowd that night were off the charts--so much energy! Check out 1/2 step--eyes and the other 1---all-time classics!

Thanks Thank you Scott and Jimmy and both Matt’s for getting this aud up, Sounds great to one who was there, This recording has the the pizazz and verve that was evident in the arena that night. Phil and Donna were outstanding. Such a good time we had at SUNY Brockport after the show also , the combination of this band and LSD and good friends……..
